# Entity

## Person

### Attribute

| name        | type     | multiplicity | DBカラム名           | DBカラム型 | 外部連携属性名     |
|-------------+----------+--------------+----------------------+------------+--------------------|
| id          | entityid | 1            | person_id            | TEXT       | external_id        |
| displayName | name     | 1            | person_display_name  | TEXT       | display_name_ext   |
| age         | age      | ?            |                      | INTEGER    |                    |
| body        | text     | ?            |                      | TEXT       |                    |
